Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.62,0:00:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓人覺得涼快的系列
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.24,0:00:10.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白色的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.11,0:00:12.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刨冰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.41,0:00:15.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杏仁豆腐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.85,0:00:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白熊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.85,0:00:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fs42}白熊：鹿兒島縣產的雪糕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.48,0:00:22.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好熱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.59,0:00:20.33,*Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白色的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.44,0:00:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 衛星導航顯示的地點是深淵的對面
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.18,0:00:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候 耳邊突然響起了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.05,0:00:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「掉下去就好了」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.72,0:00:39.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣 覺得涼快一點了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.82,0:00:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太可怕了啊 伊織
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.26,0:00:46.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦啊阿真 今天我沒法一個人睡覺了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.53,0:00:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬天的馬特洪峰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.72,0:00:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西伯利亞的暴風雪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.14,0:00:54.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想想…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.18,0:00:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全空白的日程表
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.77,0:01:04.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某種意義上 那才是最涼快的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.25,0:01:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壞掉的空調
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.42,0:01:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破爛空調
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.59,0:01:11.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,派不上用場的空調
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.47,0:01:13.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後天就會有人來修理了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.37,0:01:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.88,0:01:19.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真美和我就快要融化 變成怪獸海多隆了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.46,0:01:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心靜自然涼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.98,0:01:30.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 各位 我買冰淇淋來了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.81,0:01:36.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,復活了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.82,0:01:36.33,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剪刀石頭布
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.91,0:01:38.57,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.48,0:01:41.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我老家稍微走幾步路就是海邊了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.76,0:01:45.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真懷念美麗海啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.76,0:01:45.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fs42}我那霸響老家沖繩的一處大海名，原名為美ら海
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.23,0:01:47.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大海嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.55,0:01:52.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,製作人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.32,0:01:55.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是大海啊 大海
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.06,0:01:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慰勞旅行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.52,0:02:01.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 我們想去慰勞旅行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.76,0:02:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要突然就無理取鬧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.60,0:02:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦 不也挺好的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.37,0:02:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,福利待遇 促進健康
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.83,0:02:10.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些也是製作人的分內事喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.80,0:02:19.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就在日程表可允許的範圍內
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.39,0:02:22.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.01,0:03:57.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,0)\frz270\fn@方正准圆_GBK\bord2\be10\alpha255\fs75\pos(63,411)}和大家一起度過
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.01,0:03:57.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,0)\bord2\be10\alpha255\fs70\pos(348,535)}的{\c&H9C6200&\fs120}暑假
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.04,0:04:02.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來只準備招呼沒有工作的人來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.78,0:04:05.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果全部都來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.59,0:04:08.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實際上就是很閒 沒辦法啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.39,0:04:09.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,律子也是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.46,0:04:10.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.45,0:04:15.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有一個製作人的話會很辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.25,0:04:18.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起旅行真是很開心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.72,0:04:20.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 確實
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.97,0:04:23.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是美人魚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.49,0:04:27.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 千早 我烤了餅乾喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.30,0:04:29.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.44,0:04:30.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.74,0:04:33.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳看起來很開心呢 春香
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.26,0:04:35.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 因為這可是大海喔大海
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.68,0:04:37.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亮晶晶的波浪喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.89,0:04:40.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小春春 我們用這個跟妳換
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.10,0:04:41.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用手持的巧克力2個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.85,0:04:44.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,召喚小春春的餅乾4個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.67,0:04:47.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 太沒禮貌了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.92,0:04:49.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.04,0:04:51.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都是朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.97,0:04:54.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 要去海邊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.36,0:05:01.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好險
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.44,0:05:10.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貴音 妳差不多也該買副眼鏡戴了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.54,0:05:18.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔細一看 原來車窗上有無數的手印
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.16,0:05:20.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.44,0:05:21.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明都已經擦過了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.76,0:05:24.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是有一個無論如何都擦不掉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.61,0:05:29.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要說為什麼的話 因為只有那個是從內側印上去的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.21,0:05:32.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安靜一點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.38,0:05:43.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是大海啊
