Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.10,0:07:19.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 也許就是因為現在這樣才能開心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.10,0:07:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.60,0:07:24.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.66,0:07:42.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.85,0:07:44.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.81,0:07:47.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得來海邊 一起游泳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.68,0:07:50.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對游泳不怎麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.28,0:07:52.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟大家一起玩的話很開心的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.61,0:07:54.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來來 把上衣脫掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.69,0:07:57.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看嘛看嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.39,0:07:58.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等啦 春香
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.20,0:08:01.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了啦 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.50,0:08:03.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.60,0:08:06.13,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 別著急春香
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.76,0:08:07.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家這麼要好 真讓人欣慰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.06,0:08:08.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.45,0:08:17.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,味道很不錯
