Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.33,0:08:22.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,銀色的大胃王女啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.31,0:08:25.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4個4個 他的黑麵包
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.43,0:08:33.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位小姐 妳好可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.77,0:08:35.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是搭訕啊搭訕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.07,0:08:36.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳是從哪來的啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.68,0:08:38.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是妳喔 是美希啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.68,0:08:38.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fs42}美希讀作miki 妳=君讀作kimi正好相反
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.11,0:08:40.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.21,0:08:42.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳的話搞不好能成藝人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.50,0:08:44.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.80,0:08:47.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確如果是美希的話應該能當上呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.68,0:08:48.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.11,0:08:52.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 這個給妳 和我們一起吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.18,0:08:54.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起那邊 還是來我們這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.33,0:08:55.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些都給妳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.35,0:08:58.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.37,0:09:03.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就跟最先遊到對岸的人一起吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.93,0:09:04.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼遠？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.68,0:09:05.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要上了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.05,0:09:08.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備 跑！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.63,0:09:11.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.61,0:09:13.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是小惡魔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.27,0:09:25.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 阿響？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.69,0:09:27.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓到了呱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.18,0:09:37.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太陽看起來好大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.71,0:09:41.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 沒忘記東西吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.25,0:09:43.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.02,0:09:48.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 真的沒忘記嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.05,0:10:03.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 早就猜到會這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.20,0:10:06.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 預算…
