Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.52,0:10:19.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 不要擅自就…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.18,0:10:24.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎遠道而來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.07,0:10:26.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給您添麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.76,0:10:31.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.33,0:10:35.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.67,0:10:42.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,榻榻米睡起來很舒服的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.16,0:10:45.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算所有人都睡這裡 也很寬敞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.50,0:10:47.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好安心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.55,0:10:50.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頻道好少啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.51,0:10:52.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貴重品放這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.06,0:10:58.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 哈姆藏是貴重品呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.49,0:11:02.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓 不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.04,0:11:05.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露天泳池
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.04,0:11:06.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混浴…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.37,0:11:08.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來不是 嘖
