Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.79,0:11:33.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？那個計劃…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.18,0:11:45.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.96,0:11:48.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.68,0:11:50.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有很多 可以隨便添喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.71,0:11:57.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…很好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.56,0:12:02.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在野外吃飯別有風味呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.28,0:12:05.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貴音 我替妳拿點什麼吧
