Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.15,0:12:11.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真美還要香腸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.40,0:12:15.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也要好好吃蔬菜啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.88,0:12:18.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓妳也先去吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.48,0:12:20.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真不好意思
