Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.39,0:12:27.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了 還得添木炭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.67,0:12:31.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就…來 請用吧
