Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.60,0:12:42.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.27,0:12:46.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說美希 這是給製作人的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.25,0:12:48.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美希妳自己去烤啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.53,0:12:50.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美希是專門負責吃的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.78,0:12:51.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.88,0:12:58.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…製作人 這是飲料
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.38,0:13:01.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就給我啤酒
