Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.87,0:13:52.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.50,0:13:56.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還大浴場呢 改名叫小浴場比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.85,0:13:58.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍之水流
